categories: Category:Star Wars Battlefront II voice actors

nodes.text: Rachel Butera (born January 28, 1972) is an American actress who voices General Leia Organa in the Resurrection DLC of Star Wars Battlefront II. Butera was set to voice the character in Star Wars Resistance. However, following fan backlash over a controversial Twitter post, she was ultimately replaced by voice actress Carolyn Hennesy.
